For each client using Process H, is_on_demand_active must be set to TRUE in muse_client_references for auto-diffusion to trigger after Factset response integration. Currently only TPA has this enabled. Other clients (APE, ESY, etc.) will need this set to TRUE when they complete parallel run onboarding.

To test the full auto-diffusion flow locally without waiting for onboarding:


UPDATE own_83650_muse.muse_client_references
SET is_on_demand_active = TRUE,
    updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
WHERE client_label = 'APE';


